e, offering endless replayability. Dodge, weave, and strategize in this adrenaline-fueled game, where your skill determines your survival. Are you ready to DodgeALL?", "short_description": "DodgeALL is an adrenaline-fueled VR game that tests your reflexes in immersive 3D environments. With physics-based gameplay, each level is a new challenge. Can you weave, dodge, and survive in an arena where everyone is throwing things at you?"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://dodgeall.com/PrivacyPolicy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "GlennerooVR LLC", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.dodgeall.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "459781504968480"}, {"id": "1592192974313489"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "7267329153368602"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 3, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1747941336000929"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1251385075979902"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1231507447541804"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1231507447541804"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1735498800, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1747941336000929"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "8263487893752718", "version": "0.40.7.2"}, "id": "2493148167513843", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false